    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_plan-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "みんなはもう、目当ての場所に出発したみたいだな\n沖縄を満喫して来てくれたらいいんだが……あれ？",
      "startTime": 4.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さんじゃないですか～\nこんな所で会うなんて、奇遇ですね",
      "startTime": 12.8026534081,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 273.33354950000023,
          "startTime": 9.9359867414
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "奇遇も何も、同じ旅館に泊まっているんですが……\nfranさんは観光に行かないんですか？",
      "startTime": 20.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "今ちょうど、出るところだったんですけど\n{user}さんが一人でいるのが見えたので",
      "startTime": 25.6014519692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ！　せっかく行き合わせたことですし\n時間があるなら、一緒に国際通りでも見て回りません？",
      "startTime": 31.8014519692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "franさんが俺を誘うなんて、めずらしいですね\nまさか、何か企んでいたり……",
      "startTime": 40.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "ぎくっ……ち、違いますよ。勝手の分からない所に\n一人で行くのが、ちょっと不安なだけです",
      "startTime": 47.5967583339,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ラスベガスでは結構大変な目に遭いましたしね……\nお役に立てるか分かりませんが、ご一緒しますよ",
      "startTime": 55.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "やった！\nそれじゃ、今日はよろしくお願いしますね",
      "startTime": 60.4181191762,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastreet-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ～沖縄って賑やかですね\n大通りを歩くだけでも、楽しいです",
      "startTime": 69.7181191762,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastreet-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 64.9181191762
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 64.6835208417
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastreet-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱりいろんな物を見るのは大事ですね\n新しいデザインのインスピレーションが湧いてきそう",
      "startTime": 76.3847858429,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ははは……次に衣装をデザインする時は\n経費を使い込まないで下さいね……",
      "startTime": 83.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastreet-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それより、そろそろお腹が空いてきませんか？\nあ、ここのお店なんて美味しそうですよ",
      "startTime": 91.9818835259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "あら……なんだか店内がバタバタしてますね\n人気店なのに、人手が足りてないのかしら",
      "startTime": 101.8152168592,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10046.989522200007,
          "startTime": 106.7666666684
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 96.3818835259
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 96.1719113828
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "ま、いいか。私達もさっさと注文しちゃいましょう\nえーっと、どんな料理があるのかしら……",
      "startTime": 110.1485501926,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5509.303998999996,
          "startTime": 110.5818835259
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "なーべーらーんぶしー？　ぱぱいや……いりちー？\n名前だけじゃどういう料理か全く分かりませんね……",
      "startTime": 123.2485501926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ここに説明が書いてありますよ\nゴーヤの味噌煮とパパイヤの炒め物みたいです",
      "startTime": 129.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ……でも、料理は凄く美味しそうですけど……\nカロリーもお値段も可愛くないですね",
      "startTime": 138.9639924368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "沢山食べたいのはやまやまなんですが……\n私はさんぴん茶と、この豆腐の料理だけにしておきます",
      "startTime": 145.8973257702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "え、それだけしか食べないんですか？\nせっかく観光に来たことですし、もう少し食べても……",
      "startTime": 153.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、でも……太るのは困りますし\n恥ずかしながら……あまり持ち合わせもありませんし",
      "startTime": 162.9052852949,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そんな……せっかくの旅行ですし、今日くらい気にせず\n食べて下さい。ほら、俺も少し奢りますから……",
      "startTime": 171.7333190918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "本当に？　奢ってくれるんですか！？\nマネージャーに二言はありませんね！？",
      "startTime": 178.0854934376,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、何から頼もうかしら\nまずビールと、あ、豚の顔はマストよね",
      "startTime": 183.3484763972,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ぶ、豚の顔！？　さっきの市場でも売ってましたけど\n顔がそのまんまで、なんというかこう……",
      "startTime": 191.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02-kor017.m4a",
      "text": "その市場の人が、コラーゲンの塊だから美容にいいって\n言ってたんですよ。なら食べるしかないじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 199.797892666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_52_02-kor018.m4a",
      "text": "すみませーん、注文お願いしまーす！\nふふっ、今日は奢りだしどんどん頼んじゃおうっと",
      "startTime": 207.3666432699,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
